    <item>
      <title>法国大选的赌注在哪里？意大利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-06-24/french-elections-where-to-lay-your-bets-maybe-italian-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场对马克龙竞选口号的判断正在加强。如果巴黎极右翼或极左翼引发危机，意大利债务状况将更糟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-06-24/french-elections-where-to-lay-your-bets-maybe-italian-bonds</guid>
